Version 5.0 was ported by innotek GmbH (makers of VirtualBox and now part of
Sun Microsystems
) to run with OS/2 as host.6 For this version, innotek also developed guest extensions for OS/2 guest, that can be used with Windows, OS/2 or Mac OS X hosts using Virtual PC versions 5, 6 or 7. A new version of the guest extensions was included with Virtual PC 2004.
